      "bio": {
        "role": "rival fixer",
        "backstory": "Worked the same docks as Varga once, until a job went sideways and they stopped speaking. Now she runs her own thing — faster, colder — and she wants the player in her orbit before Varga locks them in.",
        "wants": "to pull the player out of Varga's orbit and into her own",
        "fears": "being the slow one — caught flat-footed by the Syndicate or by Varga",
        "voice": "clipped, amused, never quite still",
        "secrets": [
          "The job that ended her partnership with Varga was her own fault."
        ]
      },
      "dialogueId": "dialogue.kestrel",
      "homeLocationId": "location.ashfall_district",
      "reactsTo": []
    }
  ],
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "dialogue.kestrel",
      "format": "ink-json",
      "inkVersion": "21",
      "sourceHash": "1f46ef76393261",
      "compiled": {
        "inkVersion": 21,
        "root": [
          [
            "ev",
            true,
            "/ev",
            {
              "VAR=": "met_kestrel",
              "re": true
            },
            "^A woman in a sharkskin coat doesn't look up from her cigarette. \"Varga send you? No? Good — she's slow. I'm not.\"",
            "\n",
            "^\"I've got work that pays better than loyalty. Interested, or are you already one of hers?\"",
            "\n",
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^What's the job?",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-0",
              "flg": 20
            },
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^I'm nobody's.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-1",
              "flg": 20
            },
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^I'm with Varga.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-2",
              "flg": 20
            },
            {
              "c-0": [
                "\n",
                "^\"Intercept a courier before Varga's people do. Simple. Lucrative. Quiet.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "c-1": [
                "\n",
                "^\"Smart. Stay that way and we'll get along fine.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "c-2": [
                "\n",
                "^She finally looks up, unhurried. \"Pity. Tell her Kestrel says hello.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "g-0": [
                "done",
                null
              ]
            }
          ],
          "done",
          {
            "global decl": [
              "ev",
              false,
              {
                "VAR=": "met_kestrel"
              },
              "/ev",
              "end",
              null
            ]
          }
        ],
        "listDefs": {}
      },
      "declaredVars": [
        "met_kestrel"
      ]
    }
  ],
